Package: thor
Title: Interface to 'LMDB'
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(person("Rich", "FitzJohn", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "rich.fitzjohn@gmail.com"),
    person("The OpenLDAP Foundation", role = "cph"))
Description: Key-value store, implemented as a wrapper around 'LMDB';
    the "lightning memory-mapped database".  'LMDB' is a transactional
    key value store that uses a memory map for efficient access.  This
    package wraps the entire 'LMDB' interface, providing objects for
    transactions and cursors.
